title: 005-Everybodys.Golf.2.Multi5.EUR.PSP-crosby
description:
Special Features  

  

Tee off in Everybody&#039;s Golf tournaments with up to 16 players via Internet play
12 exotic courses including tropical islands, the arid desert, snow-capped mountains and the coast
In-depth character customisation with more than 320 options
Experience the fun of Everybody&#039;s Golf with the widely acclaimed classic gameplay
Tee off locally with up to 8 players and settle the score via Ad Hoc either head-to-head or in tournament play
Upgrade your clubs and golf balls to execute more accurate shots, longer drives, tighter approach shots and perfect putts
Perfectly suited to handheld play, whether you&#039;re filling time with a few well-placed putts, or ready to head out for a full 18 holes
